<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accès refusé - GameVault</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>🎮</text></svg>">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .error-page__code {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #ff6b81);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .error-page__icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        .error-page__title {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .error-page__text {
            color: #a0a0b0;
            max-width: 450px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .error-page__actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .error-page__btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            background-color: #e94560;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .error-page__btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff6b81;
        }
        .error-page__btn--outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #a0a0b0;
            color: #a0a0b0;
        }
        .error-page__btn--outline:hover {
            border-color: #e0e0e0;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            background-color: transparent;
        }
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-page__code { font-size: 5rem; }
            .error-page__icon { font-size: 3rem; }
            .error-page__title { font-size: 1.25rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page__code">403</div>
    <div class="error-page__icon">🔒</div>
    <h1 class="error-page__title">Accès refusé</h1>
    <p class="error-page__text">Vous n'avez pas les permissions nécessaires pour accéder à cette page. Connectez-vous ou retournez à l'accueil.</p>
    <div class="error-page__actions">
        <a href="/" class="error-page__btn">Retour à l'accueil</a>
        <a href="/login" class="error-page__btn error-page__btn--outline">Se connecter</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
